ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of JUDY A. STEELE of Halifax, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first, in the place of George Williston MacDonald, whose term has expired.
